    "name": "Memory Adventures in the Jungle Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3013270,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013270/extras/5decebf1683b393e9cd2a5ed5b9bce94.avif?t=1760347054\" width=600 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过我们的免费试用版，进入一个充满奇幻和冒险的神奇世界！在探索充满可爱和有趣动物的丛林时，测试您的记忆力和注意力……以及许多秘密！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个休闲而有趣的挑战中，您需要找到匹配的卡片并连接成对的卡片。凭借其随机生成的关卡和引人入胜的游戏玩法，此试用版是放松和磨练技能的完美方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论您是轻松有趣的粉丝还是惊险刺激的心理测试的粉丝，这款游戏都能为您带来数小时的精彩娱乐。立即试用，体验一场精彩的野外卡片匹配冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013270/extras/11f572678fa84eb176c1cb374a50d8e5.avif?t=1760347054\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用你从未知道的技能让自己惊叹不已！ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在丛林深处新奇的冒险中， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里你可以在玩乐的同时训练你的记忆力。 <br>- 收集独特的卡牌 <br>- 解锁成就 <br>- 完成关卡 <br>- 在这场史诗般的冒险中还有更多！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >~ 怎么玩 ~ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将卡片配对以将其从场上移除。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >移除所有卡牌以完成关卡。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你足够快，你将创下新的高分。 在享受乐趣的同时提高！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在简单难度下，卡片上只有：只有图像。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡片必须按以下方式配对：相同的图像。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快来展示你的技能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013270/extras/c59453653bb829498719d70535f38005.avif?t=1760347054\" width=500 height=190 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013270/extras/4ef767e6d24474f40765805480ade2f1.avif?t=1760347054\" width=500 height=138 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013270/extras/60083e74a786ed532b002016a8973add.avif?t=1760347054\" width=500 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013270/extras/06db93b540f9c08e1c45e6cb5406b810.avif?t=1760347054\" width=500 height=170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013270/extras/fe318db4b399002b21e488ef0be8014f.avif?t=1760347054\" width=500 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013270/extras/8cc105382fad550607d7648c205bd520.avif?t=1760347054\" width=500 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013270/extras/8c1ba9c66af7a72ac3de92fac1bbad7c.avif?t=1760347054\" width=500 height=168 /></span></p>",
